headline: Cognizant Included in Forbes List of the World's Best Employers 2025
summary: For the third consecutive year, Cognizant has been named one of the World's Best Employers by Forbes. This prestigious award is presented in collaboration with Statista, the world-leading statistics portal and industry ranking provider.
